column2: SELECT TOP # A.ID_#, A.Name, A.RAdeg, A.DEdeg, A.logMBH, D.t1#_arms_winding_a2#_tight_flag, D.t1#_arms_winding_a2#_medium_flag, D.t1#_arms_winding_a2#_tight_debiased, D.t1#_arms_winding_a2#_medium_debiased, D.t0#_smooth_or_features_a0#_smooth_debiased, D.t0#_smooth_or_features_a0#_features_or_disk_debiased, C.specobjID FROM MyDB.Liu2# as A CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (A.RAdeg, A.DEdeg, #/#.) AS B INNER JOIN SpecPhotoAll as C on B.objID = C.objID INNER JOIN zoo2MainSpecz as D on C.specobjID = D.specobjID WHERE D.t0#_smooth_or_features_a0#_features_or_disk_debiased> # AND D.t0#_edgeon_a0#_no_debiased> # AND D.t1#_arms_winding_a2#_tight_debiased> # AND D.t1#_arms_winding_a2#_medium_debiased> # INTO Liu2#_zoo2MainSpeczSpiral
